      <title>在Jekyll 3.0中手动添加pagination</title>
      <link href="/2018/08/16/zai-jekyll-3.0-zhong-shou-dong-tian-jia-pagination/"/>
      <url>/2018/08/16/zai-jekyll-3.0-zhong-shou-dong-tian-jia-pagination/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>使用Hyde主题，在本地查看Blog时，文章无法显示；<br>启动转化和本地服务<code>bundle exec jekyll serve</code>时会出错：</p><blockquote><p>Deprecation: You appear to have pagination turned on, but you haven’t included the <code>jekyll-paginate</code> gem. Ensure you have <code>gems: [jekyll-paginate]</code> in your configuration file.</p></blockquote><p>因为Jekyll 3中并没有集成pagination，需要手动安装。<br>1.打开终端，输入<code>gem install jekyll-paginate</code><br>2.打开项目根目录下的<code>_config.yml</code>，添加以下内容：</p><blockquote><p>gems :</p><ul><li>jekyll-paginate</li></ul></blockquote><p>保存后重新执行<code>bundle exec jekyll serve</code>即可。</p><h3 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h3><ul><li><a href="https://www.jenntesolin.com/blog/2015/10/28/fix-jekyll-pagination-upgrade-to-3/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fix pagination after upgrading from Jekyll 2 to Jekyll 3</a></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
